---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Privacy Policy - BudgetDeals India" description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8 md:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We do not collect any personal information from visitors to this website. We do not use cookies, tracking pixels, or analytics scripts that identify individual users.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Affiliate Links</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">This website contains affiliate links to Amazon.in. When you click on a deal link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps support the operation of this site and our Telegram channel.</p>
          <p class="mb-4">All affiliate links are clearly marked and redirect through our tracking domain for click counting purposes only.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We link to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Amazon.in (affiliate partner)</li>
            <li>Telegram (for our channel)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4">These third parties have their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review them.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Since we don't collect personal data, there's no personal data to secure. Our website is served over HTTPS.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We may update this policy occasionally. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">For questions about this policy, contact us via our <a href="https://t.me/budgetdeals_india" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-orange-600 hover:underline">Telegram channel</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>